(GUNFIRE)

1065
01:05:07,536 --> 01:05:08,536
(PANTING)

1066
01:05:20,349 --> 01:05:21,983
SARAH: Wow.

1067
01:05:21,985 --> 01:05:24,019
What is this place?

1068
01:05:24,021 --> 01:05:25,654
FRANK: My first safe house.

1069
01:05:27,390 --> 01:05:31,526
Untouched, since 1984. Aw!

1070
01:05:33,529 --> 01:05:35,030
(LAUGHS)

1071
01:05:38,668 --> 01:05:40,368
Fugu poison?

1072
01:05:40,370 --> 01:05:44,339
Fugu poison is deadly stuff.
Terrible death.

1073
01:05:44,341 --> 01:05:49,077
This your little gizmo?
XKG gas. I invented it.

1074
01:05:49,079 --> 01:05:51,980
We tried to take out
old Fidel Castro
in '61 in Cuba.

1075
01:05:51,982 --> 01:05:53,615
That didn't work though.

1076
01:05:53,617 --> 01:05:55,250
Any tea, Frank?

1077
01:05:55,252 --> 01:05:58,019
Why does Han
hate you so much?

1078
01:05:58,021 --> 01:05:59,487
Not enough hugs as a child.

1079
