Frank framed him
for stealing state secrets.

1080
01:06:06,363 --> 01:06:08,430
So he went from being

1081
01:06:08,432 --> 01:06:11,299
a highly decorated
counter-intel officer

1082
01:06:11,301 --> 01:06:14,703
to... (CHUCKLES)
...to being a pariah.

1083
01:06:14,705 --> 01:06:16,738
What's ironic though,
is that Frank

1084
01:06:16,740 --> 01:06:19,641
actually created
the circumstances

1085
